      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software development follows a documented quality management system with version control, unit testing, and traceability to requirements.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver has documented version control and unit test coverage, but formal traceability to device-specific requirements is incomplete. Achieved level 3 falls below the required level 4 for MRL 5."
    },
    {
