      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy testing on manufactured solutions demonstrates expected convergence rates for all governing equations.",
      "rationale": "Order-of-accuracy testing was performed for the flow solver; however, the hemolysis transport scalar equation was not independently verified. Achieved level 3 is below required level 4."
