      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation or equivalent grid convergence study performed on hemolysis index QoI with GCI reported.",
      "rationale": "Grid convergence index was computed for velocity and pressure fields; hemolysis index GCI was estimated but relied on only two mesh refinement levels rather than the required three. Achieved level 3."
    },
