    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Based on review of available simulation and experimental evidence, the CFD model is considered acceptable for predicting absolute hemolysis levels for the VAD COU. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification has been completed and predicted hemolysis index values fall below the clinical threshold across the assessed operating envelope. The assessment team concludes that the overall body of evidence is sufficient to support regulatory submission.",
